Subject: Y0185-APP0443-S: Access Denied on Azure AD Inventory scan.
Description: StealthAudit is trying to connect to ALLSTATE365.ONMICROSOFT.COM from Y0185-APP0443-S but we are getting the following: "Connecting to ALLSTATE365.ONMICROSOFT.COM using eee0e1ad-4c1a-43b7-858c-65720965b491: ACCESS DENIED" "ALLSTATE365.ONMICROSOFT.COMeee0e1ad-4c1a-43b7-858c-65720965b491ACCESS DENIED profile: Azure App Connection" Have requested confirmation of secret from the ADI team.
Solution_Comment__c:
Wrong credential profile configured. Currently, only the Application (client) ID and Client Secret value are supported to authenticate the Azure AD/Entra ID.
Modern authentication with a certificate is not supported by AZUREADINVENTORY DC
